  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>1. Store Operations Management</p><p></p><p>Oversee daily shop operations to ensure smooth and efficient workflow</p><p></p><p>Ensure compliance with company policies, SOPs, and relevant health regulations</p><p></p><p>Maintain cleanliness, hygiene, and proper storage of herbs and TCM products</p><p></p><p>Monitor opening and closing procedures and cash handling</p><p></p><p>2. Staff Supervision & Training</p><p></p><p>Supervise TCM practitioners, sales staff, and assistants</p><p></p><p>Arrange staff schedules, attendance, and duty rosters</p><p></p><p>Train new staff on product knowledge, customer service, and shop procedures</p><p></p><p>Conduct performance evaluations and provide coaching</p><p></p><p>3. Customer Service & Patient Support</p><p></p><p>Ensure high standards of customer service and patient care</p><p></p><p>Handle customer inquiries, feedback, and complaints professionally</p><p></p><p>Support TCM physicians by coordinating consultation flow and appointments</p><p></p><p>Educate customers on basic product usage (non-medical advice)</p>",
